272f3730-6886-4fc1-89db-461a148daaed.title: Adventurer Jon
272f3730-6886-4fc1-89db-461a148daaed.text: Hello <player>, what can I do for you?

options.text: Do you have any Adventure Path starter kits for me?
Can you show me some Adventure Paths?

57eeb497-8026-487f-8d14-fd3bd7d2b1ea.title: Adventurer Jon
57eeb497-8026-487f-8d14-fd3bd7d2b1ea.text:
A long time ago, I was a newbie just like you who
didn't know what to do and I would be more than
happy to pass on my experience.

610aca62-2485-4e55-b2ac-eee33732dbd0.title: Adventurer Jon
610aca62-2485-4e55-b2ac-eee33732dbd0.text:
I've created some Adventure Paths which I recommend
you to start off with. An Adventure Path is a list of
tasks which you can complete in any order.

e96fe756-d2fd-4b53-9aa2-2969870c5d56.title: Adventurer Jon
e96fe756-d2fd-4b53-9aa2-2969870c5d56.text:
To help you get started on your Adventure Path, I'll
also give you a starter kit with some useful items.

d6cf3e7b-659d-48aa-8694-0e2aeb9dd92e.title: Adventurer Jon
d6cf3e7b-659d-48aa-8694-0e2aeb9dd92e.text:
Once you've completed an Adventure Path task, come
back to me and I'll give you a reward.

c1883fc2-6087-45ba-80e1-451e2861f30e.title: <player>
c1883fc2-6087-45ba-80e1-451e2861f30e.text: Do you have any Adventure Path starter kits for me?

cc28a2bd-1eb9-4760-b1fc-7e01d401dbcd.title: Adventurer Jon
cc28a2bd-1eb9-4760-b1fc-7e01d401dbcd.text:
You seem to have already claimed all of your starter
kits.

b3ae5910-87fb-4f2b-9688-c6915991bee2.title: Adventurer Jon
b3ae5910-87fb-4f2b-9688-c6915991bee2.text: Here are all of the starter kits you have left to claim.

9263d29c-cc19-4cd6-8487-d0a9b13c42b5.title: <player>
9263d29c-cc19-4cd6-8487-d0a9b13c42b5.text: Can you show me some Adventure Paths?

8da4d209-9f9f-4a69-9f9d-a5dcbdde67d7.title: Adventurer Jon
8da4d209-9f9f-4a69-9f9d-a5dcbdde67d7.text: Safe travels adventurer, come back soon.
